Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.47,0:00:22.56,Default,,0,0,0,,JANUARY 1014 AD - OUTSKIRTS \NOF GAINSBOROUGH, NORTHEAST ENGLAND
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.64,0:00:24.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Thorkell's using it as an excuse.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.77,0:00:26.81,Default,,0,0,0,,That's the only reason I can think of.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.90,0:00:28.36,Default,,0,0,0,,But, Floki,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.82,0:00:31.32,Default,,0,0,0,,-the reports from Derby-- \N-The left flank is undermanned!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.40,0:00:33.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't underestimate a force of 500 soldiers.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.36,0:00:34.99,Default,,0,0,0,,We're talking about Thorkell's army!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.49,0:00:36.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Floki.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.57,0:00:38.12,Default,,0,0,0,,If the reports are true,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.20,0:00:40.24,Default,,0,0,0,,then your actions will be disrespectful.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.33,0:00:41.70,Default,,0,0,0,,It's impossible.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.79,0:00:46.08,Default,,0,0,0,,His Highness Canute can't be alive \Nand with Thorkell as one of his followers.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.21,0:00:49.00,Default,,0,0,0,,It's impossible!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.47,0:01:01.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Floki! Want to fight? I'll fight you.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.64,0:01:03.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Restrain yourself, Thorkell.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.52,0:01:06.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought I sent a messenger several days ago
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.73,0:01:09.69,Default,,0,0,0,,to notify you of my return, Floki.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.57,0:01:13.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you always greet your guests \Nwith spears in hand?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.78,0:01:17.32,Default,,0,0,0,,No, of course not...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.78,0:01:22.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Askeladd! Why are you here?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.29,0:01:24.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you deaf?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.21,0:01:29.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm asking you whether you're going
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.29,0:01:32.30,Default,,0,0,0,,to draw your bows against a member \Nof the royal family of Denmark.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.38,0:01:34.01,Default,,0,0,0,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.13,0:01:38.01,Default,,0,0,0,,We Jomsvikings received an inaccurate report
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.09,0:01:41.72,Default,,0,0,0,,that an enemy army was going to attack...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.18,0:01:47.39,Default,,0,0,0,,I apologize.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.02,0:01:51.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Notify the king
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.27,0:01:53.78,Default,,0,0,0,,that I shall be at his hall by evening.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.86,0:01:55.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Make sure you report accurately.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.33,0:02:09.17,Default,,0,0,0,,What in the world happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.54,0:02:12.80,Default,,0,0,0,,He's a completely different person.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.01,0:03:47.93,Default,,0,0,0,,GAINSBOROUGH CASTLE TOWN \NDANISH ARMY HEADQUARTERS
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.77,0:03:51.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone, listen to me while we walk.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.23,0:03:53.98,Default,,0,0,0,,We must not strike yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.06,0:03:55.06,Default,,0,0,0,,CROWN
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.15,0:03:57.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't have many allies within this army.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.44,0:04:01.11,Default,,0,0,0,,If we strike now, they'll label us as traitors.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.20,0:04:02.82,Default,,0,0,0,,We need time to prepare.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.82,0:04:07.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Thorkell. You betrayed them once,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.16,0:04:09.54,Default,,0,0,0,,but you're still popular among the warriors.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.62,0:04:11.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Spend time with the leaders \Nof all the clans
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.91,0:04:13.87,Default,,0,0,0,,and mend ties with them.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.21,0:04:16.04,Default,,0,0,0,,In other words, are you telling me
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.13,0:04:19.59,Default,,0,0,0,,to go drink as much as I want, \Nand that you'll pay for it?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.67,0:04:22.13,Default,,0,0,0,,As long as you invite the other leaders. \NNow, go.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.22,0:04:25.01,Default,,0,0,0,,What a wonderful order!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.47,0:04:28.51,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm so glad I decided to follow you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.60,0:04:30.27,Default,,0,0,0,,-Let's go! \N-Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.81,0:04:34.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Askeladd. Come with me to see the king.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.52,0:04:36.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to hear what you think of him.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.61,0:04:37.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Understood.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.07,0:04:40.23,Default,,0,0,0,,And about the future.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.32,0:04:41.86,Default,,0,0,0,,How will we achieve it?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.94,0:04:43.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Understood.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.49,0:04:46.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I think an assassination would be best \Nin the short run.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.99,0:04:50.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Your brother, His Highness Harald,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.37,0:04:53.54,Default,,0,0,0,,is far away in Denmark right now. \NThis is a good opportunity.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.04,0:04:56.42,Default,,0,0,0,,If the king passes away right now,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.50,0:04:58.84,Default,,0,0,0,,then command of the army in England
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.92,0:05:00.71,Default,,0,0,0,,is going to pass to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.80,0:05:05.97,Default,,0,0,0,,However, if we do so, we must hide \Nthe person responsible for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.14,0:05:11.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Thorfinn.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.43,0:05:14.98,Default,,0,0,0,,In the future, I'll assign you with other tasks \Nin addition to being a guard.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.06,0:05:16.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm counting on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.19,0:05:17.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't give me orders.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.02,0:05:20.61,Default,,0,0,0,,I never said I decided to work for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.19,0:05:24.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Please forgive him for his impertinence.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.45,0:05:27.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll make sure I instruct this idiot properly.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.20,0:05:34.25,Default,,0,0,0,,God...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.25,0:05:39.38,Default,,0,0,0,,must be watching us, even as we stand here now.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.46,0:05:43.38,Default,,0,0,0,,People losing friends,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.46,0:05:46.22,Default,,0,0,0,,and parents and children killing each other...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.30,0:05:48.80,Default,,0,0,0,,He must be looking down on everything
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.89,0:05:52.18,Default,,0,0,0,,from up high in heaven.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.81,0:05:57.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll never forgive him.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.98,0:06:03.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to create paradise on earth.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.48,0:06:05.90,Default,,0,0,0,,A peaceful and prosperous place.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.99,0:06:09.07,Default,,0,0,0,,A utopia for those who go through \Nsuffering in their lives.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.74,0:06:13.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I may not be able to achieve it in one generation,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.79,0:06:15.66,Default,,0,0,0,,but I'm still going to take
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.75,0:06:17.29,Default,,0,0,0,,the first step.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.87,0:06:21.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure that God will cherish me
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.13,0:06:23.67,Default,,0,0,0,,and summon me to his side.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.75,0:06:25.42,Default,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.51,0:06:27.84,Default,,0,0,0,,in that moment I will tell him:
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.18,0:06:32.47,Default,,0,0,0,,"We don't need heaven, nor its trials, any longer.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.55,0:06:36.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Our paradise is on earth."
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.02,0:06:42.52,Default,,0,0,0,,We're going to take back what we lost.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.52,0:06:46.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm willing to turn into a demon \Nif that's what it takes to do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.40,0:06:50.95,Default,,0,0,0,,I will help you,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.20,0:06:53.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Your Highness.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.76,0:07:10.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Welcome back.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.80,0:07:14.51,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm glad, Canute.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.81,0:07:17.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you for your kind words.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.06,0:07:21.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I lost the soldiers you had entrusted to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.40,0:07:23.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Your words are more than I deserve.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.40,0:07:26.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Come closer.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.61,0:07:29.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.49,0:07:32.99,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you think, Thorfinn?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.16,0:07:34.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, they're there.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.24,0:07:37.08,Default,,0,0,0,,About 20 of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.16,0:07:39.75,Default,,0,0,0,,There are some up high too. Archers.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.79,0:07:43.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Your Highness. It's an ambush.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.67,0:07:45.29,Default,,0,0,0,,It seems that the king
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.88,0:07:48.55,Default,,0,0,0,,knows about our intentions.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.09,0:07:53.76,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong? Without further delay, come closer.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.51,0:07:57.18,Default,,0,0,0,,You two.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.26,0:07:59.39,Default,,0,0,0,,You must not draw your swords, no matter what.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.39,0:08:02.19,Default,,0,0,0,,He who draws his sword first loses.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.44,0:08:06.36,Default,,0,0,0,,That's the type of fight this is.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.00,0:08:22.21,Default,,0,0,0,,My eyes have gotten used to the darkness.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.92,0:08:24.88,Default,,0,0,0,,If I get a little closer,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.96,0:08:26.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll be able to see the king's face.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.75,0:08:30.01,Default,,0,0,0,,If I can see his face...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.09,0:08:31.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.01,0:08:38.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Right there is fine. Kneel down.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.10,0:08:47.40,Default,,0,0,0,,His eyes are tired.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.48,0:08:49.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Is this who
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.23,0:08:51.15,Default,,0,0,0,,the king of the Danes is?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.24,0:08:52.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Askeladd.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.33,0:09:03.41,Default,,0,0,0,,What happened to Ragnar? I don't see him.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.33,0:09:06.83,Default,,0,0,0,,He died. In Mercia.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.83,0:09:11.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I see. That's too bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.17,0:09:14.76,Default,,0,0,0,,He was a loyal subject.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.43,0:09:22.98,Default,,0,0,0,,In normal circumstances, we should be \Ncelebrating your return with food and drink.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.39,0:09:26.69,Default,,0,0,0,,However,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.77,0:09:30.77,Default,,0,0,0,,I wanted to speak with you once informally.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.99,0:09:34.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Canute. Only you. Rise.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.61,0:09:38.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Walk ten steps forward.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.76,0:09:57.55,Default,,0,0,0,,You face has changed
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.63,0:10:00.55,Default,,0,0,0,,in just a short time.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.64,0:10:03.31,Default,,0,0,0,,You look like me when I was young.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.97,0:10:05.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Then
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.48,0:10:08.69,Default,,0,0,0,,you must understand what's in my heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.36,0:10:12.57,Default,,0,0,0,,You're a troublesome child.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.65,0:10:14.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I never imagined you'd become
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.86,0:10:16.45,Default,,0,0,0,,just like me, even in that regard.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.74,0:10:18.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Children
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.99,0:10:23.12,Default,,0,0,0,,grow up watching what their parents do.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.20,0:10:24.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Do not blame yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.91,0:10:28.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Long ago, when I was young,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.92,0:10:33.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I drove my father, the former king, out of this country
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.63,0:10:37.30,Default,,0,0,0,,and seized this crown.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.38,0:10:41.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I did it because I believed it was the best \Nthing to do for the kingdom.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.93,0:10:47.60,Default,,0,0,0,,The former king was cruel, but he was also a coward.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.60,0:10:53.61,Default,,0,0,0,,The world would sink into chaos if someone \Nlike him had the crown.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.69,0:10:57.74,Default,,0,0,0,,How can he say that when he's surrounded \Nby this many guards?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.82,0:10:59.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Shut up. He'll hear you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.07,0:11:04.49,Default,,0,0,0,,So, you decided not to keep up the pretense, \NYour Highness?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.16,0:11:08.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't forget you're surrounded by the enemy.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.96,0:11:12.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought that I had done something great,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.29,0:11:15.38,Default,,0,0,0,,and that I could do great things.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.84,0:11:18.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Until I put this on, that is.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.01,0:11:23.18,Default,,0,0,0,,This crown
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.26,0:11:25.97,Default,,0,0,0,,has its own will.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.31,0:11:30.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Once you wear this crown, you can command
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.35,0:11:33.02,Default,,0,0,0,,a thousand ships and 10,000 men.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.11,0:11:37.23,Default,,0,0,0,,You can take all kinds of treasure from distant lands.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.11,0:11:42.82,Default,,0,0,0,,A power like that of the gods \Nis bestowed upon you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.28,0:11:46.12,Default,,0,0,0,,However...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.62,0:11:51.04,Default,,0,0,0,,However, Canute,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.12,0:11:54.00,Default,,0,0,0,,the king isn't the one who uses that power.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.00,0:11:57.96,Default,,0,0,0,,That power is used by the will of the crown.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.72,0:12:03.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you mean
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.39,0:12:05.18,Default,,0,0,0,,the crown ordered you...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.18,0:12:07.97,Default,,0,0,0,,to kill me?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.27,0:12:14.60,Default,,0,0,0,,There are only two things that the crown \Norders the king to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.69,0:12:16.65,Default,,0,0,0,,It orders him to use his power,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.73,0:12:19.07,Default,,0,0,0,,and to increase his power.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.15,0:12:21.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Resistance is futile.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.65,0:12:26.45,Default,,0,0,0,,The crown does not want you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.18,0:12:50.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Canute.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.31,0:12:52.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll give you part of Cornwall.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.85,0:12:56.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Live your days in peace there
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.19,0:12:58.61,Default,,0,0,0,,while reading the Bible.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.44,0:13:03.78,Default,,0,0,0,,If you refuse, then you'll die here.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.20,0:13:10.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Did the crown make you say that too,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.29,0:13:12.58,Default,,0,0,0,,-Your Highness? \N-Your Highness!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.66,0:13:15.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I humbly ask you to let me speak.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.00,0:13:20.00,Default,,0,0,0,,State your name.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.34,0:13:23.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm Canute's follower,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.67,0:13:26.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Askeladd, son of Olaf.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.68,0:13:31.39,Default,,0,0,0,,With all due respect, consider whether your actions \Nare in line with the will of the crown.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.14,0:13:35.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Continue.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.10,0:13:38.69,Default,,0,0,0,,His Highness Canute
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.77,0:13:42.48,Default,,0,0,0,,stole Thorkell and the military power he commands \Naway from London.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.94,0:13:45.95,Default,,0,0,0,,If you become the king of England,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.03,0:13:49.53,Default,,0,0,0,,then London will have no choice but to surrender.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.58,0:13:54.54,Default,,0,0,0,,The wealth of London will become yours untouched, \NYour Highness.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.33,0:13:57.17,Default,,0,0,0,,His Highness Canute
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.25,0:13:59.25,Default,,0,0,0,,is the one who made the sacrifice
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.33,0:14:01.17,Default,,0,0,0,,for this great achievement.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.50,0:14:06.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it not unreasonable to punish the man who rendered \Nsuch distinguished service?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.30,0:14:07.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Your handling of this matter
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.88,0:14:09.93,Default,,0,0,0,,would deeply trouble
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.01,0:14:12.93,Default,,0,0,0,,your generals when the time comes \Nto divide the new territory.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.01,0:14:15.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Please reconsider this matter.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.31,0:14:21.40,Default,,0,0,0,,You're a man who's good with words.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.61,0:14:25.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Askeladd. "The one covered in ashes"?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.15,0:14:30.78,Default,,0,0,0,,That's your nickname.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.87,0:14:33.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Tell me the name that your father gave you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.66,0:14:38.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm only known as Askeladd.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.25,0:14:41.21,Default,,0,0,0,,My father didn't give me a name.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.88,0:14:47.22,Default,,0,0,0,,You must be the child of one of his mistresses. No...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.30,0:14:50.05,Default,,0,0,0,,You must be a child he forced one of his slaves to have.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.15,0:15:05.36,Default,,0,0,0,,What's going on? \NI've never seen Askeladd get so mad.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.57,0:15:08.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Canute.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.53,0:15:11.24,Default,,0,0,0,,You have a good follower.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.74,0:15:13.87,Default,,0,0,0,,It is just as he said.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.41,0:15:17.87,Default,,0,0,0,,I have to reward you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.04,0:15:21.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I am leaving for York tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.58,0:15:24.04,Default,,0,0,0,,There, I shall throw a banquet.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.05,0:15:27.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I shall give you your reward there.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.98,0:15:49.57,Default,,0,0,0,,My blood froze just now, Your Highness.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.61,0:15:53.11,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you so worried about?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.20,0:15:56.58,Default,,0,0,0,,As you already know, the king
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.66,0:16:00.08,Default,,0,0,0,,doesn't have enough justification to kill me right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.16,0:16:02.42,Default,,0,0,0,,He's the man who they call the wise king.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.33,0:16:05.34,Default,,0,0,0,,As long as we don't do anything reckless,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.42,0:16:08.30,Default,,0,0,0,,it's safer to lie within the king's bosom.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.09,0:16:13.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Then that's all the more reason to refrain from \Nprovoking him like you did just now.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.43,0:16:18.31,Default,,0,0,0,,It's nothing of consequence.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.64,0:16:21.52,Default,,0,0,0,,King Sweyn is a slave to the crown.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.19,0:16:26.52,Default,,0,0,0,,The power of the crown.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.61,0:16:29.23,Default,,0,0,0,,I will show him how to use it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.99,0:16:32.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Askeladd...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.99,0:16:39.37,Default,,0,0,0,,I must be wary of him.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.75,0:16:44.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Cheers!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.87,0:16:47.54,Default,,0,0,0,,All right! Don't be shy!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.63,0:16:50.34,Default,,0,0,0,,This is all on His Highness Canute!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.63,0:16:54.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Long live the prince!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.14,0:17:03.18,Default,,0,0,0,,-That's his 57th glass! \N-He's a monster!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.85,0:17:07.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! You've been drinking a lot. Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.40,0:17:10.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't remember inviting you here.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.07,0:17:14.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm Willibald. Did you forget me?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.40,0:17:15.24,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.45,0:17:18.53,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.03,0:17:21.45,Default,,0,0,0,,-Your beard is gone! \N-You look so young. How old are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.54,0:17:22.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm 23.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.66,0:17:25.00,Default,,0,0,0,,-No way! \N-You're in your early 20s?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.08,0:17:27.67,Default,,0,0,0,,All right! It's my turn next!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.75,0:17:29.17,Default,,0,0,0,,The captain is up now!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.25,0:17:31.96,Default,,0,0,0,,You're behind by 58 glasses!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.05,0:17:33.63,Default,,0,0,0,,What a strange man.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.05,0:17:37.30,Default,,0,0,0,,He does whatever he wants, \Nbut no one hates him.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.34,0:17:39.22,Default,,0,0,0,,True.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.56,0:17:43.27,Default,,0,0,0,,So? What do you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.27,0:17:46.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you think you can kill him? The king?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.02,0:17:50.90,Default,,0,0,0,,It's going to be difficult.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.98,0:17:53.28,Default,,0,0,0,,That's what I'd say.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.07,0:17:58.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I got the impression he's a smart man.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.32,0:18:02.41,Default,,0,0,0,,He's discerning, and he's a man of action \Nwho can make the first move.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.41,0:18:08.33,Default,,0,0,0,,When he saw that we wouldn't buckle under his threats, \Nhe switched to a different strategy.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.42,0:18:10.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I would say he's skilled in war.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.92,0:18:16.13,Default,,0,0,0,,No wonder he's the king of the country.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.22,0:18:17.72,Default,,0,0,0,,He's a tough opponent.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.05,0:18:23.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if we're planning to kill him someday, \NI guess now's not the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.39,0:18:27.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's submit to his wishes for the time being
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.10,0:18:29.19,Default,,0,0,0,,while we wait for our chance.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.36,0:18:32.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Your Highness! Your Highness!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.82,0:18:37.99,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm so glad you returned safely!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.07,0:18:41.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you have any idea how much I, Gunnar, \Nworried about you?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.66,0:18:44.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I apologize that I was unable to greet you at the castle.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.91,0:18:48.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I just returned from a foreign country.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.58,0:18:52.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I always believed you'd return, of course!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.34,0:18:55.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, is this gentleman over here your new follower?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.67,0:18:58.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Can you introduce me?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.22,0:19:01.72,Default,,0,0,0,,This is Ragnar's brother, Gunnar. \NPlease become acquainted with each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.80,0:19:05.97,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm Askeladd, son of Olaf.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.06,0:19:09.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, you look like a dependable character.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.48,0:19:11.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm Gunnar.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.69,0:19:13.06,Default,,0,0,0,,By the way, Your Highness...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.52,0:19:17.78,Default,,0,0,0,,that plan from a long time ago... \NThe prospects look brighter now.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.86,0:19:19.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm talking about the Duchy of Normandy.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.99,0:19:23.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I wanted to talk to you about it later \Nwith my brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.24,0:19:26.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Ragnar is dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.41,0:19:28.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry for making you go through all that trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.62,0:19:32.08,Default,,0,0,0,,And I'm not going to go into exile.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.38,0:19:34.21,Default,,0,0,0,,-Your Highness? What did you say? \N-I'm sorry
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.29,0:19:37.17,Default,,0,0,0,,to put you to the trouble of \Nrunning around to the other countries.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.80,0:19:40.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I just picked a fight with King Sweyn.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.72,0:19:43.22,Default,,0,0,0,,-Please help me. \N-My brother...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.30,0:19:44.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Gunnar.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.10,0:19:49.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Your job is to keep an eye on the king \Nand report back to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.93,0:19:52.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Choose soldiers who you trust.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.90,0:19:56.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Your Highness! You must not talk about that \Nin a place like this!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.86,0:20:00.07,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't care. This is actually a good place \Nto talk in secret.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.40,0:20:01.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Your Highness...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.07,0:20:04.87,Default,,0,0,0,,You've changed.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.20,0:20:13.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course I've changed. \NI must change everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.47,0:20:26.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Gunnar's no good.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.31,0:20:30.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't think he's as loyal to the prince \Nas he says.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.32,0:20:46.45,Default,,0,0,0,,How wonderful that you're so devoted \Nto staying prepared.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.53,0:20:49.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Doesn't your right arm hurt?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.12,0:20:50.70,Default,,0,0,0,,-Askeladd. \N-What?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.46,0:20:58.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I see. You're going home?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.30,0:21:01.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I know you said you don't care,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.92,0:21:04.34,Default,,0,0,0,,but we did betray you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.88,0:21:08.47,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know how I can face you anymore-- \NOuch!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.85,0:21:11.27,Default,,0,0,0,,I got you!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.35,0:21:15.60,Default,,0,0,0,,And look what happened to my brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.69,0:21:18.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I hope Bjorn's wounds heal.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.82,0:21:23.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Atli! And you still call yourself a Viking?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.70,0:21:27.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't believe I had such an honest man working for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.74,0:21:33.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Bjorn's not going to last long.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.33,0:21:35.37,Default,,0,0,0,,The wound reached his intestines.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.42,0:21:38.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Now,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.75,0:21:42.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Thorfinn is the only one left from among my men.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.80,0:21:44.97,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the perfect time for making a fresh start.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.14,0:21:48.43,Default,,0,0,0,,A bracelet?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.51,0:21:50.05,Default,,0,0,0,,It's gold. Take it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.22,0:21:53.14,Default,,0,0,0,,What? I don't need it! There's no reason for me to take it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.22,0:21:55.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Just take it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.10,0:21:57.73,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no such thing as having too much money \Nwhile traveling.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.57,0:22:05.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry. I appreciate it.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.11,0:22:05.95,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.03,0:22:09.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! Are you going to give it to me or not?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.70,0:22:10.95,Default,,0,0,0,,I have one condition.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.87,0:22:15.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Never pick up a sword ever again.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.16,0:22:17.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Swords don't suit you, Atli.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.79,0:22:20.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Raise some sheep, get a wife,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.25,0:22:22.46,Default,,0,0,0,,have a kid, and die in your bed.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.50,0:22:27.18,Default,,0,0,0,,If I see you on the battlefield in the future, \NI'm going to kill you,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.26,0:22:28.72,Default,,0,0,0,,even if you're on my side.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.22,0:22:32.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay. I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.98,0:22:45.53,Default,,0,0,0,,-What's that? \N-This?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.61,0:22:47.61,Default,,0,0,0,,It's something important.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.70,0:22:48.99,Default,,0,0,0,,It's pretty.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.83,0:22:59.62,Default,,0,0,0,,That's too expensive! Give me a discount.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.71,0:23:01.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Show me some younger women!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.38,0:23:03.21,Default,,0,0,0,,-Bring the younger women! \N-Any takers?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.29,0:23:05.46,Default,,0,0,0,,FEBRUARY 1014 AD - YORK, DANISH \NARMY-OCCUPIED TOWN, NORTHUMBRIA REGION
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.64,0:00:24.40,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,トルケルの方便だ！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.77,0:00:26.81,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,他には考えられん！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.90,0:00:28.36,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,し…しかしフローキ様。
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.82,0:00:31.32,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,ダービーからの報告では…\N左翼が薄いぞ！！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.40,0:00:33.28,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,兵500とて侮るな！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.36,0:00:34.99,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,相手はトルケル軍だ！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.49,0:00:36.49,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,フローキ様。
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.57,0:00:38.12,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,報告が事実ならば、
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.20,0:00:40.24,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,このなさりようは大変不敬な…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.33,0:00:41.70,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,あり得ぬ！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.79,0:00:46.08,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,あのクヌート殿下がトルケルを従えて生還するなど、
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.21,0:00:49.00,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,決してあり得ぬ！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.47,0:01:01.56,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,ようフローキ。戦る気か？相手になるぜ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.64,0:01:03.35,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,控えよトルケル
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.52,0:01:06.65,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,私が帰還する旨、
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.73,0:01:09.69,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,数日前に使者を送ったはずだぞ。フローキ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.57,0:01:13.69,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,槍をもって出迎えるのが貴様の礼か？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.78,0:01:17.32,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,い…いえ。そのようなことは決して…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.78,0:01:22.20,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,アシェラッド！？なぜ貴様が…！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.29,0:01:24.50,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,耳が聞こえぬのか貴様
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.21,0:01:29.21,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,貴様はデンマーク王家に対し…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.29,0:01:32.30,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,弓を引く気かと訊いているのだ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.38,0:01:34.01,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,あ…い…いえ、その…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.13,0:01:38.01,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,わがヨーム戦士団は…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.09,0:01:41.72,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,敵軍襲来との誤報を受けまして…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.18,0:01:47.39,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,申し訳ありませぬ…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.02,0:01:53.78,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,王陛下の館へ夕刻までに参じると報告しておけ。
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.86,0:01:55.24,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,正確にな
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.33,0:02:09.17,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,一体何が…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.54,0:02:12.80,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,まるで別人ではないか…！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.77,0:03:51.14,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,全員歩きながら聞け
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.23,0:03:53.98,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,今はまだ仕掛けてはならぬ。
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.65,0:03:57.48,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,私の味方はこの軍中に少ない
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.44,0:04:01.11,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,ただ手向かえば反逆者となろう。
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.20,0:04:02.82,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,手回しの時間が要る。
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.82,0:04:07.08,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,トルケル。そなたは一度裏切ったが、
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.16,0:04:09.54,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,今も戦士たちに人気がある。
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.62,0:04:11.83,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,各部族の首領たちと交わり、
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.91,0:04:13.87,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,関係を修復しておけ
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.21,0:04:16.04,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,つまりあれかい？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.13,0:04:19.59,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,アンタのおごりでジャカジャカ酒飲めってこと？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.67,0:04:22.13,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,他の首領を誘ってだぞ。行け
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.22,0:04:25.01,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,すっっばらしい命令だ！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.47,0:04:28.51,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,アンタについてきて正解だったぜ
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.60,0:04:30.27,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,行くぞぉ！あっ！おい！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.81,0:04:34.44,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,アシェラッドは私と共に王のところだ。
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.52,0:04:36.52,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,そなたの人物評を聞きたい
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.61,0:04:37.48,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,はっ
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.07,0:04:40.23,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,それと今後だ。
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.32,0:04:41.86,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,いかに事を運ぶ
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.94,0:04:43.40,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,はっ…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.49,0:04:46.12,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,短期的には暗殺がよろしいかと
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.99,0:04:50.29,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,兄王子ハラルド殿下は
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.37,0:04:53.54,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,遠くデンマークにいらっしゃいます。これは好機です
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.04,0:04:56.42,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,今王陛下が崩御されれば、
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.50,0:04:58.84,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,イングランド方面軍の最高指揮官は
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.92,0:05:00.71,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,あなた様ということに
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.80,0:05:05.97,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,この場合…首謀者を偽装する必要がありますが…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.14,0:05:11.35,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,トルフィン。
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.43,0:05:14.98,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,今後は護衛以外にも働いてもらうことになるだろう。
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.06,0:05:16.10,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,頼むぞ
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.19,0:05:17.94,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,命令すんな。
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.02,0:05:20.61,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,オレァあんたの手下になった覚えはねぇ
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.19,0:05:24.36,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,ご無礼お許し下さい。
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.45,0:05:27.57,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,このバカへは私から指図しておきます
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.20,0:05:34.25,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,神は…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.25,0:05:39.38,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,こうしている今も、我々を見ていらっしゃるのだろうな
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.46,0:05:43.38,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,友を失い、
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.46,0:05:46.22,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,親と子が殺し合う…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.30,0:05:48.80,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,そんな様の全てを、
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.89,0:05:52.18,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,天空の高みから見下ろしておられるのだろう
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.81,0:05:57.06,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,許せぬ
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.98,0:06:03.40,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,私はこの地上に楽土を作るぞ。
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.48,0:06:05.90,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,平和で豊かな、
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.99,0:06:09.07,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,生きることに苦しむ者たちの理想郷を…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.74,0:06:13.70,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,私の代では成し得ぬかもしれぬ。
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.79,0:06:15.66,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,それでも最初の一歩を、
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.75,0:06:17.29,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,私が踏み出すのだ
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.87,0:06:21.04,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,神はきっと私を愛で、
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.13,0:06:23.67,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,御許へ召そうとするだろう
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.75,0:06:25.42,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,だが…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.51,0:06:27.84,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,その時私はこう言うのだ
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.18,0:06:32.47,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,“もはや天の国も試練も要らぬ。
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.55,0:06:36.02,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,我々の楽土は地上にある”とな
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.02,0:06:42.52,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,我々が失ったものを取り戻すのだ。
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.52,0:06:46.57,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,そのためには…鬼にもなろう
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.40,0:06:50.95,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,お手伝いいたします。
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.20,0:06:53.37,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,殿下
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.76,0:07:10.59,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,よくぞ戻った…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.80,0:07:14.51,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,うれしいぞクヌート
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.81,0:07:17.98,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,ありがたきお言葉。
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.06,0:07:21.31,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,陛下よりお預かりした兵を失ってしまった。
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.40,0:07:23.11,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,不肖の身に余ります
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.40,0:07:26.11,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,近う寄れ
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.61,0:07:29.95,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,お待ち下さい。
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.49,0:07:32.99,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,どうだ？トルフィン
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.16,0:07:34.78,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,フン。居るな
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.24,0:07:37.08,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,20人ってところか。
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.16,0:07:39.75,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,高い所にもだ。弓兵だな
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.79,0:07:43.25,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,殿下…伏兵です。
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.67,0:07:45.29,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,どうやら王陛下は、
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.88,0:07:48.55,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,こちらの腹をお察しのようですな
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.09,0:07:53.76,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,どうした？早う寄らぬか
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.51,0:07:57.18,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,そなたたち。
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.26,0:07:59.39,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,何があっても剣を抜いてはならぬぞ。
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.39,0:08:02.19,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,先に抜いたほうの負けだ。
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.44,0:08:06.36,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,これは…そういうケンカだ
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.00,0:08:22.21,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,暗さに目が慣れてきたな。
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.92,0:08:24.88,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,もう少し近づけば…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.96,0:08:26.75,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,王の顔がわかる。
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.75,0:08:30.01,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,顔を見れば…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.09,0:08:31.34,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,止まれ
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.01,0:08:38.64,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,そこでよい。ひざまずけ
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.10,0:08:47.40,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,疲れた眼だ。
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.48,0:08:49.15,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,これが…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.23,0:08:51.15,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,デーン人の王か
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.24,0:08:52.40,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,アシェラッド
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.33,0:09:03.41,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,ラグナルはどうした。姿が見えぬが
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.33,0:09:06.83,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,死にました。マーシアの地にて
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.83,0:09:11.17,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,そうか…それは惜しいな
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.17,0:09:14.76,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,あれは誠の忠臣であった。
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.43,0:09:22.98,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,本来なら酒肴をもって帰還を祝うべきだが…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.39,0:09:26.69,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,一度そなたとは…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.77,0:09:30.77,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,形式抜きで話をしたいと思うておった
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.99,0:09:34.86,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,クヌートのみ立て。
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.61,0:09:38.66,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,10歩前へ進め
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.76,0:09:57.55,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,ほんのわずかの間に…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.63,0:10:00.55,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,顔がかわったな。
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.64,0:10:03.31,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,余の若き日に似ておる
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.97,0:10:05.39,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,されば…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.48,0:10:08.69,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,我が心の内もおわかりでございましょう
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.36,0:10:12.57,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,困った子だ…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.65,0:10:14.78,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,そのようなところまで
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.86,0:10:16.45,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,余に似るとは…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.74,0:10:18.91,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,子は
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.99,0:10:23.12,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,親の為し様を見て育つのです。よもや…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.20,0:10:24.83,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,お責めになりますまいな
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.91,0:10:28.83,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,かつて若き日…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.92,0:10:33.96,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,余は父である先王を国外へ追い放ち
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.63,0:10:37.30,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,この王冠を奪った。
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.38,0:10:41.72,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,それが王国のためによき事と信じたからだ。
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.93,0:10:47.60,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,先王は性残忍にして臆病者だった。
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.60,0:10:53.61,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,そのような者が王冠を戴いては世が乱れる
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.69,0:10:57.74,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,こんだけの護衛に囲まれて何言ってやがる
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.82,0:10:59.82,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,黙れ。聞かれるぞ
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.07,0:11:04.49,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,腹芸を使う気はねェってかい、殿下よ…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.16,0:11:08.66,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,敵の巣の中にいるってことを忘れなさんなよ…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.96,0:11:12.21,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,よき事を成した。
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.29,0:11:15.38,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,よき事を為せると思うておった
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.84,0:11:18.51,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,これをかぶるまではな…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.01,0:11:23.18,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,意志があるのだ。
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.26,0:11:25.97,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,この王冠にはな
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.31,0:11:30.27,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,かぶれば千の船、
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.35,0:11:33.02,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,万の兵を統率できる。
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.11,0:11:37.23,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,遠国のあらゆる宝を取り寄せることができる
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.11,0:11:42.82,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,神々がごとき力が身に宿る
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.28,0:11:46.12,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,だが…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.62,0:11:51.04,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,だがクヌートよ。
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.12,0:11:54.00,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,力を使うのは王ではない。
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.00,0:11:57.96,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,王冠の意志が使うのだ
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.72,0:12:03.30,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,王冠が
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.39,0:12:05.18,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,陛下に命じたというのですか。
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.18,0:12:07.97,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,私を殺せと
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.27,0:12:14.60,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,王冠が王に命じるのはただふたつ。
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.69,0:12:16.65,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,力を使うことと、
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.73,0:12:19.07,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,力を増やすことだ。
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.15,0:12:21.49,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,抗うても無駄なことよ。
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.65,0:12:26.45,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,王冠は、そなたを欲してはおらぬ
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.18,0:12:50.02,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,クヌート。
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.31,0:12:52.98,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,そなたにコーンウォールの一部をやろう
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.85,0:12:56.10,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,そこで聖書でも読みながら
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.19,0:12:58.61,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,平穏の日々を送るがよい
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.44,0:13:03.78,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,いやだと申すなら…この場で死ぬがよい
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.20,0:13:10.20,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,そのお言葉も王冠が言わせているのですか。
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.29,0:13:12.58,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,陛下\N陛下！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.66,0:13:15.42,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,おそれながら発言をお許し下さい！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.00,0:13:20.00,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,名乗れ
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.34,0:13:23.22,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,クヌート様の従士。
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.67,0:13:26.01,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,ウォラフの子、アシェラッドと申します
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.68,0:13:31.39,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,失礼ながら、果たしてこの御沙汰は王冠の意志にかないましょうや！？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.14,0:13:35.48,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,続けよ…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.10,0:13:38.69,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,王子殿下は
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.77,0:13:42.48,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,ロンドンよりトルケルという戦力を奪い取りました
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.94,0:13:45.95,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,陛下がイングランド王にご即位なされれば…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.03,0:13:49.53,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,彼の町には降伏より他、道はありませぬ
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.58,0:13:54.54,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,ロンドンの富は、無傷のまま陛下のものとなります
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.33,0:13:57.17,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,多大なる犠牲を払い、
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.25,0:13:59.25,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,この戦果をもたらしたるは
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.33,0:14:01.17,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,クヌート殿下に他なりません
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.50,0:14:06.22,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,功労ある者が罰せられる道理がありましょうか。
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.30,0:14:07.80,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,この御沙汰…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.88,0:14:09.93,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,新たな領地の割譲において、
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.01,0:14:12.93,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,各将軍に動揺を与えます
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.01,0:14:15.18,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,何卒…ご再考を！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.31,0:14:21.40,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,口のまわる男だ。
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.61,0:14:25.86,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,アシェラッド…“灰まみれ”か…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.15,0:14:30.78,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,それはあだ名であろう。
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.87,0:14:33.74,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,貴様の父が授けた名を申せ
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.66,0:14:38.16,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,ただ…アシェラッドと。
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.25,0:14:41.21,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,父は私に名を与えませんでした
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.88,0:14:47.22,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,妾の子か…いや…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.30,0:14:50.05,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,奴隷に産ませた子かの？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.15,0:15:05.36,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,なんだ！？アシェラッドがここまで怒るなんて…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.57,0:15:08.45,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,クヌート…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.53,0:15:11.24,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,よい従士を持っておるな。
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.74,0:15:13.87,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,そやつの申すとおりだ
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.41,0:15:17.87,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,そなたたちには褒美をやらねばならんな
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.04,0:15:21.50,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,余は明日ヨークに発つ。
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.58,0:15:24.04,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,彼の地にて宴席を設ける
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.05,0:15:27.21,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,褒美はそこで授けよう
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.98,0:15:49.57,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,肝を冷やしましたぞ殿下
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.61,0:15:53.11,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,何を慌てることがある
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.20,0:15:56.58,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,そなたの察するとおり…王には今、
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.66,0:16:00.08,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,私を殺すだけの大義名分がない
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.16,0:16:02.42,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,賢王と呼ばれたいお方なのだ。
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.33,0:16:05.34,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,こちらさえ軽挙に出ねば、
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.42,0:16:08.30,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,王の内懐はむしろ安全だろう
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.09,0:16:13.43,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,ではなおのこと先ほどのような挑発はお控え下さい
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.43,0:16:18.31,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,なんのことはない。
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.64,0:16:21.52,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,スヴェン王は王冠の奴隷というわけだ。
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.19,0:16:26.52,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,王冠の力…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.61,0:16:29.23,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,私が使いこなしてみせようぞ
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.99,0:16:32.70,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,アシェラッドか…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.99,0:16:39.37,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,少々警戒せねばならんな…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.75,0:16:44.79,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,カンパーイ！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.87,0:16:47.54,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,さあ！ジャンジャンやってくれ！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.63,0:16:50.34,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,全部クヌート殿下のおごりだぜ！！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.63,0:16:54.30,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,殿下バンザーイ！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.14,0:17:03.18,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,57杯目だ！\Nバケモンだコイツー！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.85,0:17:07.94,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,おーい！さっきからガブガブガブガブ飲みやがって。誰だおめェは？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.40,0:17:10.98,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,坊主なんざ招いた覚えねーぞ？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.07,0:17:14.32,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,私はヴィリバルドです。お忘れですか？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.40,0:17:15.24,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,は？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.45,0:17:18.53,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,いーっ！？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.03,0:17:21.45,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,あのヒゲの！？\N若いな！いくつだよ！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.54,0:17:22.58,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,23です
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.66,0:17:25.00,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,うそだろ！？\N20代前半！？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.08,0:17:27.67,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,よーし！次はオレが相手だ！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.75,0:17:29.17,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,大将のお出ましだ！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.25,0:17:31.96,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,ハンデ58杯っすよ！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.05,0:17:33.63,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,不思議な男だ。
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.05,0:17:37.30,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,好き放題に生きながら、周りの者に憎まれぬ
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.34,0:17:39.22,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,はァ
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.56,0:17:43.27,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,で…どうだ。
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.27,0:17:46.81,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,殺れそうか？あの王を
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.02,0:17:50.90,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,難しい…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.98,0:17:53.28,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,と言わざるを得ませんな
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.07,0:17:58.11,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,頭の良いお方とお見受けしました。
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.32,0:18:02.41,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,洞察力と先手を打つ行動力をお持ちです。
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.41,0:18:08.33,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,我々が脅しに屈さぬと見るや、次の手に転ずるあたり…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.42,0:18:10.92,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,戦上手とも申せましょう
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.92,0:18:16.13,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,さすがは一国の王、といったところでしょうか。
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.22,0:18:17.72,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,手強いですぜ
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.05,0:18:23.31,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,いずれ殺すにしても今ではない…か
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.39,0:18:27.02,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,ま。当分は王陛下のスキを窺いつつ、
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.10,0:18:29.19,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,恭順の体でいきましょう
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.36,0:18:32.57,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,殿下！殿下！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.82,0:18:37.99,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,無事のご帰還、お喜び申し上げます！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.07,0:18:41.57,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,このグンナル、どれほどに心配したことか！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.66,0:18:44.83,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,ご入城にお出迎えもせず、申し訳ございません。
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.91,0:18:48.50,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,なにぶんたった今！異国より帰って参ったものですから。
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.58,0:18:52.25,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,もちろん、きっとのご生還信じておりましたぞ！おや、
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.34,0:18:55.59,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,こちらの御仁は新しい従士殿でございますか？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.67,0:18:58.13,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,ご紹介頂けますかな？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.22,0:19:01.72,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,ラグナルの弟、グンナルだ。見知りおけ
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.80,0:19:05.97,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,ウォラフの子、アシェラッドと申します
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.06,0:19:09.39,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,ほぉ！なんとも頼もしい風格ですな。
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.48,0:19:11.60,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,グンナルと申す
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.69,0:19:13.06,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,ところで殿下…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.52,0:19:17.78,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,かねてよりの計画…メドが立ち申した。
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.86,0:19:19.90,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,ノルマンディー公国です。
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.99,0:19:23.24,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,その件について、兄も交えて後ほど…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.24,0:19:26.33,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,ラグナルは死んだ
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.41,0:19:28.62,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,私のためにすまぬことをしたな
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.62,0:19:32.08,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,それから…亡命はせぬ
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.38,0:19:37.17,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,殿下…なんと申された…\Nそなたが諸国を奔走してくれていたことは大儀であった。
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.80,0:19:40.63,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,先ほどスヴェン王にはケンカを売ってきた。
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.72,0:19:43.22,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,そなたも力を貸せ\Nあ、兄者が…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.30,0:19:44.14,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,グンナル
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.10,0:19:49.85,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,そなたの仕事は、王の監視と報告だ。
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.93,0:19:52.56,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,使う兵は信用できる者を選べ
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.90,0:19:56.77,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,殿下！そっ…そのような話を、こんな所で…！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.86,0:20:00.07,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,かまわぬ。むしろこの場は密談によい
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.40,0:20:01.78,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,殿下…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.07,0:20:04.87,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,お変わりになられた…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.20,0:20:13.04,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,変わるさ。全てを変えてゆかねばならぬ
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.47,0:20:26.97,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,あのグンナルってのはいかんなァ。
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.31,0:20:30.48,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,口ほど殿下への忠心があるとも思えんし…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.32,0:20:46.45,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,予習復習に余念のないことで。
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.53,0:20:49.04,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,右腕、痛くないのかねェ？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.12,0:20:50.70,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,アシェラッド\Nあ？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.46,0:20:58.21,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,そうか…故郷に帰るか
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.30,0:21:01.84,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,アンタは気にしねェと言ってくれたけど…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.92,0:21:04.34,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,やっぱオレたちゃ裏切り者だし…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.88,0:21:08.47,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,なんつーか…この先どのツラして会やいいのか…\N痛で！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.85,0:21:11.27,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,当たった～！ハハハッ！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.35,0:21:15.60,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,なんか…兄者もあんなんなっちまったし…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.69,0:21:18.31,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,ビョルンの傷…治るといいな…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.82,0:21:23.61,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,アトリ。おめェそれでもヴァイキングかよ？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.70,0:21:27.66,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,よくもまァこんな真人間がオレの手下になったもんだぜ
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.74,0:21:33.25,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,ビョルンは長くもたねェよ。
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.33,0:21:35.37,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,傷がはらわたまで達してる
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.42,0:21:38.67,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,これでもう
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.75,0:21:42.71,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,昔からの手下はトルフィンだけってことになるな。
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.80,0:21:44.97,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,再出発にゃちょうどいい
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.14,0:21:48.43,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,腕輪？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.51,0:21:50.05,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,金だ。持ってけ
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.22,0:21:53.14,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,えぇ！？いっ、いらねェよ！もらう理由がねェ！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.22,0:21:55.02,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,いいから受け取れ。
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.10,0:21:57.73,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,路銀が多くて困るこたァねェだろが
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.57,0:22:05.03,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,sすまねェ…じゃあ…ありがたく…ん？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.11,0:22:05.95,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,あれ？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.03,0:22:09.62,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,なんだよ！？くれんのかくれねェのかどっちだよ！？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.70,0:22:10.95,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,条件がある
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.87,0:22:15.08,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,二度と剣を握るな。
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.16,0:22:17.46,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,おめェにゃ似合わねェ。アトリ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.79,0:22:20.17,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,羊を飼い嫁をもらって
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.25,0:22:22.46,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,ガキをこさえてベッドで死ね
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.50,0:22:27.18,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,これから先、おめェを戦場で見かけた時は…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.26,0:22:28.72,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,味方でも斬るぞ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.22,0:22:32.97,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,あァ…わかった
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.98,0:22:45.53,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,それなに？\Nん？これか？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.61,0:22:47.61,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,こりゃあ大切な…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.83,0:22:59.62,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,高ェよ！まけろ！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.71,0:23:03.21,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,もっと若い女出せよ若い女ァ！
